## Security Architecture

1. **Auth:** JWT (7 days expire) + bcrypt (10 rounds)
2. **Validation:** Client + Server
3. **Rate Limiting:** 5 req/min (AI), 5 req/15min (Auth)
4. **HTTPS:** Production only (Nginx reverse proxy)

